<p class="ql-align-center">旁边的小电视机电视柜音箱和落地灯</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">房间虽小，也有小客厅内味了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>﹀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201214/0b3ac29212ed4b019d69cf785ff4c69a.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小小的走廊</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">开发出了餐厅厨房两个功能区</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小户型真香！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>﹀</strong></p>
