<p class="ql-align-center">床边再铺上一张床边毯</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是精致男孩本孩了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>﹀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201214/555dd05630224519922d227890f38b28.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">床头柜用储物箱代替</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">储物功能非常棒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>﹀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">宜家再次出镜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>﹀</strong></p>
